display.title: Iridium and Osmium
description: This part of the chain starts by obtaining some &&aRarest Metal Mixture&&r.
You'll need at least an &&9IV&&r &&3Large Chemical Reactor&&r, but the average power draw isn't too bad.

&&dChlorine&&r is fully looped, and &&dHydrogen&&r is slightly negative &&7(&&ounless you put Acidic Osmium Solution in the Distillation Tower and electrolyze the water back... &&8on second thoughts, don't do that&&r&&8).
&&aIridium&&r is required to progress through &&9IV&&r, so get your PGS line automated ASAP!
